# Times — Prayer Times App

Offline-first Islamic prayer times for **Android and iOS only**. Package: `com.intizamia.times`.

## Stack

- **Flutter** + **Material 3** (green seed: `Color(0xFF2E7D32)`)
- **flutter_bloc** for state (not Riverpod)
- **go_router** with bottom `NavigationBar`
- **adhan_dart** for local prayer calculation
- **i18n:** English (default), Urdu, Arabic (RTL for ur/ar)

## Navigation

1. Prayer Times — main timetable; **Setup** CTA if method/location not configured
2. Coming Soon — placeholder middle tab
3. Settings — full calculation and app preferences

## Locked decisions

- First run: user **must** choose calculation method (no silent default)
- Notifications MVP: **system default** sound only
- Middle tab: localized "Coming Soon"
- Read `docs/PROGRESS.md` at session start; update when completing work

